<HEADLINE> S. Africa to Demonstrate Advanced Gunships in </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, October 23 (Xinhua) -- South Africa will
demonstrate its newly developed Rooivalk attack helicopters in
Algeria in the next few days, Denel, the manufacturer of the
gunship announced today.
</P>
<P>
Denel spokesman George Masoek said this was not a marketing
exercise. "We are merely demonstrating the Rooivalk at the
request of the Algerian defense force," he said, noting that no
arms deal was being negotiated at this stage.
