Jihad said today that "the Aqsa Mosque is a red line, the
Jerusalem is a red line, and all things related to our religion
and honor are red lines" that could never be crossed.
</P>
<P>
It compared the Palestinians to volcanos that might erupt
whenever their feelings, honor, holy sites and religion were
offended.
