<HEADLINE> Korda beats Rios in Stuttgart Open </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, October 24 (Xinhua) -- Petr Korda of Czech Republic beat
Marcelo Rios of Chile to enter the semi-finals of the Stuttgart
Open tennis tournament on Friday.
</P>
<P>
