champion and third-seeded Patrick Rafter of Australia or unseeded
American Todd Martin.
</P>
<P>
The defeat is a blow to Rios' hope of entering the eight-man
ATP Tour World Champioships next month. Only Pete Sampras,
Michael Chang of the United States and Rafter have already
qualified for the championships. 
