<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, October 24 (Xinhua) -- World Boxing Council heavyweight
champion Lennox Lewis was considering a title defence against
Americans James Douglas or Lou Savarese, the Briton's manager
Frank Maloney said Friday.
</P>
<P>
