<HEADLINE> Agenda for Edinburgh Commonwealth Summit </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
EDINBURGH, October 23 (Xinhua) -- The following is the main
agenda for the four-day Commonwealth Heads of Government Meeting
(CHOGM) to be held in Edinburgh from Friday:
</P>
<P>
Friday 24 October 1997

0900  Meeting of Ministerial Group on Small States

1400  Opening ceremony

1600  First Executive Session of CHOGM
</P>
<P>
Saturday 25 October

0930  Second Executive Session of CHOGM

1300  Launch of Commonwealth South Asia Investment Fund

1500  Third Executive Session of CHOGM
</P>
<P>
Sunday 26 October
</P>
<P>
Heads of delegation depart Edinburgh for St Andrews
for the Retreat
</P>
<P>
Monday 27 October

0930  Fourth Executive Session of CHOGM

1400  Concluding Press Conference by British Prime Minister
Tony Blair and the Commonwealth Secretary General Emeka
Anyaoku 
</P>
