<HEADLINE> 60 Enterprises on Sale </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 24 (Xinhua) -- Sixty State firms were
available to investors at a trade fair in northeast China's
Liaoning Province, said today's China Daily.
