<P>
Zhuanghe Power Machinery Building Plant was one of the two
enterprises in Zhuanghe, a city under the administration of
Dalian, sold the first day of the auction on Wednesday. A private
firm based in Shenyang bought the plant for four million yuan
(481,000 US dollars).
</P>
