in metallurgy, machinery, chemicals, construction materials and
light industries, they are major tax-payers to local coffers.
</P>
<P>
Last month, Zhuanghe sold 15 State-owned firms to some private
investors. Mayor Yao Jiakai said the government will be strict
when choosing buyers concerning their capital strength and
management ability. 
